  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>If you book to stay here between the 21 May - 24 Jun you'll stay on an all inclusive board basis where a buffet breakfast, lunch and dinner are included. With lunch and dinner one bottle of water and one bottle of wine are included. You'll also be able to take full advantage of an open bar at Le Kentie Bar between 11am - 10pm daily, where selected drinks are included in the price so you can enjoy options like <span>grappa, myrtle liqueur, Limoncello, draft beer, soft drinks, water, tea, coffee and cappuccino.</span></p>
<p>Between the 25 Jun - 02 Sep you'll stay on a full board basis, which includes a buffet breakfast lunch and dinner in the hotel's main restaurant (drinks are not included).  </p>
<p><strong>Restaurant Centrale </strong>is the hotels main restaurant. </p>
<p><strong>Restaurant Belvedere</strong> (upon reservation, with supplement)</p>
<p><strong>Piano Bar</strong> Six evenings a week you can enjoy live piano music accompanied by a glass of wine. </p>
<p><strong>The Beach Bar</strong> is located right on the beach and is a lovely spot to enjoy a cool refreshing drink after soaking up the Sardinian sun.  </p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
