  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>Sant'Elmo Beach Hotel is located near Castiadas, on what's arguably one of the most stunning stretches of coastline in <a data-udi="umb://document/cc3361d2d7a945d38852da5e20516d75" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc3361d2d7a945d38852da5e20516d75}" title="Southern Sardinia">Sardinia</a>. You'll find you're never far from beautiful white sandy beaches and clear blue water. The hotel has its own private stretch of beach too, so you can chill out on your own sun lounger and make the most of the idyllic surroundings. If you fancy a change from the beach, the hotel's pool has an equally tranquil setting amidst the flower gardens. There are plenty of deck chairs and umbrellas for you to use, dotted about the place. </span></p>
<p><span>While you're here why not check out some of the activities available - they offer everything from tennis to football, seasonal kids clubs and junior clubs. There's something to keep everyone entertained. In the evenings, choose from two onsite restaurants, Centrale, which is included for all guests, or the quieter Belvedere (payable locally). Both serve a range of local and international dishes. Two bars mean you’ll have somewhere to relax after your meal before retreating to your comfortable room, which you’ll find decked out in a typical Sardinian style.</span></p>
<p>Car hire is recommended for this hotel. Sant'Elmo Beach Hotel is approx. 1 hour 5 mins from Cagliari airport.</p>]]></description>
