  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Pools &amp; Beaches</strong></span></p>
<p>The large outdoor swimming pool is immersed in the hotels gardens and equipped with <span>deckchairs and sun-umbrellas. Please note that the use of a swimming cap is mandatory. Pool towels are available for a local charge. </span></p>
<p>The hotel is set beside a long sandy private beach. The hotel offer a beach service with one umbrella and two loungers per room from the fourth row. Beach service rows one to three are payable locally. For t<span>hose looking for a more secluded spot, there are many bays to explore. </span></p>
<p><strong><u>Activities</u></strong></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="text-decoration: underline;"></span>Mini Club for children aged 4-11 from 04 Jun - 10 Sep</li>
<li>Children's Play Area</li>
<li>Daily evening entertainment 04 Jun - 10 Sep</li>
</ul>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>General Facilities</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li>Free WiFi</li>
<li>Parking</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
