  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Cottage Rooms </strong>are about 18m² and can sleep 2-3 people in double or twin beds and an extra single sofa-bed or cot (approx. €10 per day, payable locally). These rooms are located in the terraced houses on the ground floor with views of the park. They are decorated in a fresh Mediterranean style with tiled floors. They have a patio area equipped with sun chairs and  table, shower, air conditioning, TV, safe, minibar, telephone and a hairdryer. </p>
<p><strong>Family Rooms </strong>are about 24m². These rooms can sleep 3-4 people in double or twin beds with two extra single beds on a mezzanine level suitable for children aged 11 years and under. These rooms are decorated in a classic style, have park or pool views and a private patio. </p>
<p><strong>Single Occupancy Standard Rooms </strong>are about 16m² and are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
